sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Author
    participant API as Post API
    participant PS as Pub/Sub
    participant GW as WS Gateway
    participant F as Follower client

    A->>API: POST /posts
    API->>PS: notify followers rooms (batched)
    PS->>GW: events
    GW-->>F: {type: "new_post", post_id}
